{"tid":196762,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 廣東話Westbrook主題曲 ] 直到西書的盡頭","createTime":"2017-04-11T13:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T10:31:35.000Z","uid":47374,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d77753fd7f39f89e0ce5275309f0098414f7304a","tid":196762,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/214055_08ec19dcf749890218ffc57b0108e646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F214055_08ec19dcf749890218ffc57b0108e646.jpg&h=8814d072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1836182699968033/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Frealcoach%2Fvideos%2F1836182699968033%2F&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=743e6dca\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1836182699968033/</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------<br />\n原：直到世界的盡頭（男兒當入樽）<br />\n詞：正宗教練<br />\n唱：戴晉揚Mark Tai<br />\n<br />\n起西書廟比佢<br />\n望個癲佬 拯救呢隊<br />\n我晚晚裝香比佢<br />\n賀佢完成宏大壯舉<br />\n<br />\n神話紀錄又再突破<br />\n其實佢仲教曉我<br />\n唔入再射過<br />\n唔劣啲高手最怕熄火<br />\n<br />\n以往個個串爆佢射完未<br />\n唔留手 緊有佢道理<br />\n就算炒粉 永無避忌<br />\n唔會死狗 無thur晒皮<br />\n<br />\n佢嘅數據爆到究極離地<br />\n頹勢扭轉 靠佢傲氣<br />\n用每一口氣<br />\n同强隊收窄實力距離<br />\n唔係KD可婫美<br />\n成咋香 裝比你<br />\n<br />\n痛過再戰以往錯敗埸地<br />\n神勇西書 我撐硬你<br />\n被咖哩哥 猛咁做忌<br />\n唔淆底 想報復有期<br />\n<br />\n殺到上去再無退後餘地<br />\n嚟到Playoff 要有掟企<br />\n就要爭口氣<br />\n從前失足過後又再嚟<br />\n成棟西書廟等你<br />\n全部Fans等你<br />\n<br />\n留定叉燒比你"},{"pid":"a81287fa2d8feb13dc93b679004987cd3c7a05bc","tid":196762,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"909aaa7971d1e34c5b8690eda88b9fa8d5cf27eb","tid":196762,"uid":74149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/